SNB’s Hildebrand Says Swiss Growth to Weaken in Second Half

-- B y   K l a u s   W i l l e
-- 
2011-09-29T17:04:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/snb-s-hildebrand-says-swiss-growth-to-weaken-in-second-half.html
Switzerland ’s economic growth will
slow down in the second half of 2011, Swiss National President
Philipp Hildebrand said at an event in Geneva today.  The cap on the franc of 1.20 versus the euro introduced on
Sept. 6 helped lower the risk of a recession, Hildebrand added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
